candidates.body:
---
name: 'ngsPETSc'
---

# Description
Switching from ngs2petsc (no longer maintained) to ngsPETSc.
This reduces the lines of codes to maintain in Firedrake and allows for new features, including:

1. high order meshes;
2. PETSc transformation applied to Netgen mesh;
3. Quad mesh;
4. Anisotropic mesh refinement;

